creations-chat 2021-06-19 10:10:52 <@!803292176418078720> <@!723940197456281640> so the features are :-

2-Working elevons and rudder (to control during landing)
3-Internal Lights for illumination 
4-Tank and Boosters seperate
5-side hatch for crew entry on orbiter can open/close
6-boosters has tiny pusher motor that show smoke effect during seperation
7-landing gears can open and have functional and realistic gear doors
8-Main engines has mach cone (exhaust) effect
9-drogue chute deployable during landing (after touchdown)
10-Canadarm in cargo bay 
11-cargo bay doors can open
12-Control joysticks in cockpit move when turning/rolling
13-tank has smoke effect on top nose vent when stationary a pad
14-SRB(booster) nozzles also gimbal during flight
15-Can perform the real shuttle flight trajectory during launch and landing
16-Body flap (below main engines also moves during flight)
now the details:-
1-there is complete realistic shuttle interior
2-there are beds inside mid deck and a washcloset
3-external tank has piping and attachment port details
4-boosters have external details such as colour variation on nosecone
5-docking port is dockable and crew can move through in both horizontal and vertical position
6-the trails on side of each wing appear when doing sharp manuevers 
7-there are tiny wiring and segment details inside cargo bay 
8-bay doors have radiator panels too
this concludes the features and a few details , i could not remember the rest sorry for that
